node.text: After trying to pitch my show idea for the past few years, I decided to take things into my own hands and independently create a scripted podcast! This was such a journey but a lesson to never wait for opportunity…sometimes you just have to go out & create it 🙌🏼 Thank you to everyone who was part of it, can’t wait for you all to hear it this Winter!
